data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, well- kept home in Upper Pottsgrove located in the Boyertown School District! This property was maintained by the original owner since this the property was built.  The property features three large bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and one 1/2bath. Take a walk around the home and notice the size of the driveway, and the rear yard! Just think of all the hosting and summertime parties you can have with that beautiful inground swimming pool! EP Henry Patio with gas burning fireplace, and an additional patio perfect for another patio set and lawn chairs! Pool was properly winterized and maintained by the same pool company for years and have records on file. The family room/ basement was being remodeled. the carpentry, electric and HVAC is all finished in this room. It does still need walls, floors paint and trim. The price is reflected for the work needed. The home sits on .06 acre and has plenty of frontage for the kids to play and run around. the street is quite and set back off of the main roads with a spectacular view in the rear of the hills in the surrounding area. Come check it out for yourself and become the second owner of this beautiful home! Please Summit highest and best offers by Tuesday, January 30 by 5:00pm .
